      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that it's a lot, but i feel fine and i don't really have time to wait for a doctor's appointment and blood work right now. if i just do it for like 4 weeks to get a \"loading dose\" and then drop back down to a normal amount, isn't that basically what people do for severe deficiency anyway? it seems like a lot of extra hassle for something that acts like a vitamin.",
